attributes.review: im so disappointed and disgusted at this app 🤬😡 first of all, it took FOREVER TO DOWNLOAD, I began the download process 69 days ago, and it just completed. on top of that, it automatically deleted half of my apps in order to make room for it 😭 i had to enter my social security number, phone number, address, age, weight, height, gender, ethnicity, fingerprints, name of my pet goldfish, and my dog’s NUDES in order to move on to the rest of the app 😡🤬😤 after successfully getting into the app, the FBI showed up at my house and took my DOG AND WHEN I ASKED WHY THEY SAID THAT THE PRESIDENT WAS INTERESTED IN “wHaT mY dOg hAd tO oFFeR hIM” I MISS MY DOG GIVE HIM BACK 😭😭😭 I’ve been getting weird spam phone calls and emails about toe fungus cream ever since I downloaded the app EVEN AFTER DELETING IT 😔 and this morning a ransom note was left for my dog AND FISH demanding $7 billion dollars worth of McDonald’s and Cheeto dust 😭😭😭 I DONT HAVE THAT KIND OF MONEY HOW AM I SUPPOSED TO GET MY PETS BACK‼️ all in all, downloading this app will RUIN YOUR LIFE 🤬 all they want is your information and pets 😭

attributes.review: I downloaded this app in hopes to understand what was going to happen this November and what his plan was. THAT IS NOT THIS APP. This is messy, horribly constructed and there’s these pictures of a strange orange with tiny hands all over this app which is not what I download it for!! Now it’s sending me notifications to go to public gathers where people don’t wear masks and are yelling. It’s actively putting me in harms way! DO NOT DOWNLOAD at risk for your own safety and sanity!
